title: Homemade Goodies by Roz
description: A cozy kosher, non-dairy bakery with vegan choices such as scones, challah, challah rolls, raspberry almond thumbprint cookies, Mexican wedding cookies and a variety of cupcakes. The same flavors are available in birthday, special occasion and wedding cakes, sizes ranging from 6" to full sheets to tiered cakes. Plenty of seating. Free Wi-Fi.
